# LLM configuration -- copy to .env and fill in ONE of the options below.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Option 1: IBM Cloud AI (ICA)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ICA_API_KEY=your-ica-api-key
# ICA_BASE_URL=https://servicesessentials.ibm.com/apis/v3
# ICA_MODEL_ID=global/anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929-v1:0
# ICA_TIMEOUT=300

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Option 2: OpenAI
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-key

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Notes
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# - With neither key set, the pipeline runs in deterministic mode using the
#   keyword-based fallbacks built into every agent. All tests run in this
#   mode (136 passing as of the cleanup pass).
# - The Streamlit app reads .env at startup via python-dotenv (ui/app.py).
# - Tracing always writes to data/traces.db locally; no cloud setup required.
